  <description><![CDATA[<h2><span class="TextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8">The charming city of Bergen sits on the waters edge. Freckled with multi-coloured houses, it's the perfect place for sightseeing, walking and day tripping. Balestrand on the other hand, is a retreat to nature with its peaceful location on the shores of the Sognefjord. </span></span></h2>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8">This is a fantastic multi-centre holiday for those wanting </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8">to experience the city of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen" data-anchor="#">Bergen</a> and then go on to seek out nature in </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377}" title="Balestrand" data-anchor="#"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW209676786 BCX8">Balestrand</span></a><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8">. There's plenty to do in Bergen, from exploring museums and galleries to day-tripping to somewhere new.</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8"> All the while, Balestrand is an escape to nature with stunning scenery and</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW209676786 BCX8"> a slower pace of life.</span></span></p>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Guide price from: £1,332.00pp*</span></h3>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Your multi-centre holiday options:</span><span data-contrast="auto"> </span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></h3>
<ul>
<li>A choice of durations in your chosen hotels</li>
<li><span data-contrast="auto">Any day arrivals</span></li>
</ul>
<h3><span data-contrast="auto">Your holiday includes</span></h3>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Return flights from the UK</span></li>
<li>Return airport transfers (direct) to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Transfers between your chosen destinations<span data-contrast="auto"></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Twin Room at Thon Hotel Bristol Bergen, Bergen, and 3 nights in a Twin View Room at Knives Hotel, Balestrand with ferry transfers between resorts, departing on the 1st of June 25 from London Gatwick airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 21/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
